  "title": "Prime Mover Driver",
  "description": "<p><strong>Responsibility</strong></p><ul><li>Loading and discharging of chemicals at various plants and terminals.</li><li>Local Delivery of Chemicals and Base Oil products to various plants.</li><li>Empty collection of Containers/ ISO Tanks to yard, empty imports or trucking of offhire containers.</li><li>Laden Import/ Exports from various customer sites to/from PSA or Jurong Port.</li><li>Observe safety measure during operation (HSSE).</li></ul><p><strong>Requirement</strong></p><ul><li>Class 4/5 driving license and have experience driving prime mover</li><li>Minimum 3 to 5 years similar experience</li></ul>",
